{"id":"27f9779b94563ff70fa060b7c37a5629e6cb0ee4","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1229012","title":"感觉每天都有 codex 重置的帖子，雷同的内容是否有必要出现了就发一下呢","site_name":"Info Flow","source":"V2EX (创意工作者社区)","byline":"isAK47","excerpt":"OpenAI - @isAK47 - 经常看到类似的帖子，感觉挺频繁的，欢迎理性讨论。","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div id=\"Main\">\n                \n                \n<div><p>经常看到类似的帖子，感觉挺频繁的，欢迎理性讨论。</p></div>\n\n<!-- SOL tip topic -->\n\n\n\n\n\n<div>\n    <div><P><a href=\"/tag/内容\"><li></li> 内容</a><a href=\"/tag/重复\"><li></li> 重复</a><a href=\"/tag/讨论\"><li></li> 讨论</a></P><p><span>7 replies &#160;<strong>•</strong> &#160;2026-07-22 17:22:03 +08:00</span>\n    </p></div>\n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17891745\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5bdf/44ad/21529_normal.png?m=1732809027\" alt=\"fkdtz\" data-uid=\"21529\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>1</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/fkdtz\">fkdtz</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 12:31:27 +08:00\">22h 37m ago</span>  &#160; <span><img src=\"/static/img/heart_20250818.png?v=c3415183a0b3e9ab1576251be69d7d6d\" width=\"14\" alt=\"❤️\"> 1</span>\n                    \n                    <p>我也没搞懂这帮人什么心态<br>重置了对于不用 codex 的人没有影响，对于用 codex 的人自然知道重置了也不用你提醒啊<br>可能纯是闲的没事干找乐子？</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17891913\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/262bfdefba98c83c81ec6e3d561d28e5?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"Msxx\" data-uid=\"234769\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>2</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/Msxx\">Msxx</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 13:28:29 +08:00\">21h 40m ago via Android</span> \n                    \n                    <p>水贴而已</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17892554\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/06b8/e0c9/104939_normal.png?m=1708680914\" alt=\"wonderfulcxm\" data-uid=\"104939\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>5</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/wonderfulcxm\">wonderfulcxm</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 15:24:58 +08:00\">19h 43m ago via iPhone</span> \n                    \n                    <p>希望可以出一个“codex 重置”节点，然后一键屏蔽该节点 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/agAJ0Rd.jpeg\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/agAJ0Rd.jpeg\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a></p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17893017\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f33f846983bd473b33710ab6cf97422d?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"Yuk1ne\" data-uid=\"671037\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>6</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/Yuk1ne\">Yuk1ne</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 16:34:23 +08:00\">18h 34m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>还真是，今天重置了发一下，如果还没重置也发一下，终于重置了再发一下</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17893296\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ee6b/6972/702695_normal.png?m=1752593230\" alt=\"lca261224\" da